  <h1>About T2YD</h1>
  <p>T2YD is a lightweight transport management platform built to connect shippers with transporters. It supports lorry listings, delivery requests, real-time tracking, and Stripe-powered payments.</p>
  <h2>Key Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Browse and list lorries</li>
    <li>Create and manage deliveries</li>
    <li>Real-time tracking with Socket.IO</li>
    <li>Session-based authentication and role-based dashboards</li>
    <li>Stripe integration for payments (optional)</li>
  </ul>
  <p>For questions, visit the <a href="/contact">Contact</a> page.</p>
